comments: Adebayo (MIA) makes contact to Lopez's (MIL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Robinson (MIA) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) as he receives the entry pass in the post and affects his FOM.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) does not release his free throw attempt within ten seconds.
Lopez (MIL) moves forward into Butler (MIA) and initiates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) moves to the side of Holiday (MIL) while he is airborne and incidental contact occurs during the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) reaches in and makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that affects his shot attempt near the basket.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) takes more than two steps after gathering the rebound.
Ariza (MIA) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) reaches in as he defends Butler (MIA) in the post and makes clean contact with the ball that causes it to become loose.
Butler (MIA) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) engage in incidental contact while pursuing the loose ball.
Dragic (MIA) and Middleton (MIL) engage in incidental contact while pursuing the loose ball.  Both players get their hands on the ball and a held ball is correctly called.
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Dragic (MIA) is standing inside the three-point arc before the release of Antetokounmpo's (MIL) free throw attempt.
Butler (MIA) boxes out Lopez (MIL), who initiates contact to Butler's face and dislodges him from his position during the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly has his arm around Ariza (MIA) as the two players come together, but they quickly disengage.
Butler (MIA) makes contact to Lopez's (MIL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
DiVincenzo (MIL) is in a legal guarding position when he contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.  Any marginal contact is created by Butler.
Dragic (MIA) steps on the sideline out of bounds after he receives the pass.
